## ZENNER Hessware Python Access Library

This repository can be used as an example to how to access the ZHW Cloud.

## Usage

Specify your secrets inside the secrets.json file, use secrets.json.template as
an example how to use this file.

## Most relevant scripts

### gateway_getstatistics.py

Print statistics like online / offline or switching operations.

### gateway_installFirmware.py

Install a new firmware version on a gateway.

### sensor_generate_geomap.py

Print the last geo postions of a sensor to the stdout. The output can be imported into maps or qgis.

### sensor_last_values.py

Pretty print the last sensor values in a table.

### sensor_send_downlink.py

Send a downlink to a given sensor.

### switchingpoint_switch.py

Set the value of an actor.

 
